experiments.name: DenseNet121_Chexpert_BCE_E3_B32_C0_N12_NoAug_UZEROES_D256_DS9505_2LR1_LF5_SGD_Upsampled
experiments.description:
Trained DenseNet121 architecture using the 'Chexpert_BCE_E3_B32_C0_N12_NoAug_UZEROES_D256_DS9505_2LR1_LF5_SGD_Upsampled' benchmark. The benchmark was initialized for the chexpert_full dataset with batch size of 32, shuffle set to True and images rescaled to dimension (256, 256).
The training was done for 3 epochs using the SGD optimizer and custom_binary_crossentropy loss.
A total of 12 labels/pathologies were included in the training and encoded using the 'uzeroes' method.
The traing set included 268152 number of sample, the validation set 11596, and the test set 234.
